data.description: Great location in Horseshoe Bay proper! This cozy duplex has a nice entrance and several patios where you can sit in the evening and enjoy your coffee in the morning.  Take your pick of primary bedrooms as both are similar in size and each have an attached bath and sliding doors to separate patios. The open-concept floor plan includes a gorgeous stone fireplace between the living room and dining room and a perfect kitchen for entertaining. With plenty of windows, this home gets plenty of light inside! It is surrounded by a private yard with mature trees and two garages for extra storage. The low annual POA dues include access to the city park and pickleball courts and the lovely Quail Point Lodge where you can enjoy concerts, festivals, and activities most days of the week. No monthly HOA! It needs some TLC and is ready for the next owners to make it shine.   Sold AS IS. Easy to show, so call your agent to schedule a showing today!
